@@WCentral Market â West Deck@@N~
@@WThe Central Market is the commercial and social center of the
Causeway Quarter, built on an elevated stone deck that puts vendors
at eye level with the causeway population. @@WThe west deck holds
the permanent stall assignments â weavers, pot-sellers, preserved
food vendors, and the always-contested spice row. @@WArrival from
