archive challenge ledger~
@@pThe archive challenge ledger contains a systematic documentation of discrepancies between
the authorized Paradise Thesis and the full-text draft the Ledger Clerks maintain. Each
entry cites the page, the line, and the passage in the draft that contradicts the authorized
version. The last entry, in fresher ink, cites the Kel'Shadra witnessing office records and
adds: 'See testimony tube. Root tunnel. G.L.C. Vol. 91, entry 43.'
~
