testimony tube~
@@pThe testimony tube's label carries the notation code for a deposition transferred to Kel'Shadra
during the witnessing office period, cross-referenced in Garden Ledger Vol. 91, entry 43. The
tube has been resealed at least once after its original closure â the wax layers are different
colors. Someone brought it back from wherever it was sent. The contents have never been formally
re-entered into the public Ledger.
~
